main event: A UFO report from July 1959 in Switzerland with 1 photo depicting a landscape with no visible human figures.
interesting points: The report is from the Foreign Technology Division of the AFSC.
The photo shows a body of water surrounded by mountains and clouds, possibly where the UFO was sighted.
The report indicates that there was foreign technology involved in the sighting.
No human face or figure is visible in the photo, suggesting the focus was on the landscape where the UFO was observed.
The fact that the report is unclassified may indicate a higher level of credibility.
